         <category>Deletions Modifications</category>
         <ttm:title>Delete Labor Category and/or Service Offerings</ttm:title>
         <ttm:desc>Use the Delete Labor Category and/or Service Offering Modification to narrow the scope of your business' Products and Services within the terms of the Contract Offer. Note that Deletion Modifications fall under the category known as &quot;Rapid Action Modifications.&quot; This means a Contractor can submit a Deletion Modification Request and the Contracting Officer can approve it without having to go through the Signature process.
         </ttm:desc>
      </metadata>
