   <body xml:id="thebody" style="defaultCaption">
      <div xml:lang="en">
         <p begin="00:00:02.03" end="00:00:04.96" region="speaker">Removing labor categories and service offerings is a</p>
         <p begin="00:00:04.96" end="00:00:07.43" region="speaker">natural part of a business maturing.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:07.43" end="00:00:09.76" region="speaker">The business community should always be aware of</p>
         <p begin="00:00:09.76" end="00:00:11.56" region="speaker">current services.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:11.56" end="00:00:13.10" region="speaker">Enter a detailed description of your</p>
         <p begin="00:00:13.10" end="00:00:15.50" region="speaker">request, and identify the product you would like</p>
         <p begin="00:00:15.50" end="00:00:18.46" region="speaker">removed from your schedule.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:18.46" end="00:00:21.33" region="speaker">You can also provide the CO with some information</p>
         <p begin="00:00:21.33" end="00:00:23.66" region="speaker">as to why you are removing this product from your</p>
         <p begin="00:00:23.66" end="00:00:25.10" region="speaker">schedule.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:25.10" end="00:00:27.86" region="speaker">Deletion modifications fall under the category</p>
         <p begin="00:00:27.86" end="00:00:30.63" region="speaker">known as &quot;Rapid Action Modifications&quot;.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:30.63" end="00:00:32.80" region="speaker">This means that a contractor can submit a</p>
         <p begin="00:00:32.80" end="00:00:35.10" region="speaker">Deletion Modification request and the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:35.10" end="00:00:37.73" region="speaker">Contracting Officer can approve it without having</p>
         <p begin="00:00:37.73" end="00:00:40.43" region="speaker">to go through the signature process.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:40.43" end="00:00:42.93" region="speaker">When you have finished click &quot;Save and continue&quot;</p>
         <p begin="00:00:42.93" end="00:00:44.93" region="speaker">button.</p>
